result.name: prescription-cost-analysis-england
result.notes: Prescription Cost Analysis (PCA) provides details of the number of items and the net ingredient cost of all prescriptions dispensed in the community in England. The drugs dispensed are listed by British National Formulary (BNF) therapeutic class.

organization.description:

It was previously called 'The Health and Social Care Information Centre (HSCIC)'
